{"tid":2447653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美卿防長訪日韓 強化軍事同盟","createTime":"2021-03-15T10:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T10:49:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d08ed7f7ee67782452f8fc837dee67ccfdef46ae","tid":2447653,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/SFI4EULPERFZ3F6KTT4TZ7PVUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FSFI4EULPERFZ3F6KTT4TZ7PVUQ%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=c6edd5df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FSFI4EULPERFZ3F6KTT4TZ7PVUQ%2F&h=d4219136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/SFI4EULPERFZ3F6KTT4TZ7PVUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n美卿防長訪日韓 強化軍事同盟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q4zCKrPKQALUK76Bfadi49DxTgk=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4KY5QOUHLNDMFA4447E3ZHMZQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq4zCKrPKQALUK76Bfadi49DxTgk%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4KY5QOUHLNDMFA4447E3ZHMZQM.jpg&h=4627e299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國防長奧斯汀將訪問亞洲。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【劍指中國】美國國務卿布林肯和國防部長奧斯汀今日展開亞洲之旅，將先後訪問盟友日本和南韓。美國兩大文武官員首次外訪便聯袂出訪日韓，奧斯汀出發前不諱言此行是要強化亞州的軍事同盟，劍指中國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rIzcfV_6z8xMJyn6TSncZoaObOM=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BAX4F6YBANBVRKLCLQ6X6L3JBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrIzcfV_6z8xMJyn6TSncZoaObOM%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBAX4F6YBANBVRKLCLQ6X6L3JBM.jpg&h=d28325e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國務卿布林肯上任後首訪日韓和印度。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美日將譴責華入侵釣島<br />\n<br />\n「我們的目標是要確保有軍事能力和作戰準備&hellip;&hellip;可以對中國或任何欲挑戰美國的國家構成可信的威懾力。」奧斯汀在總部設在夏威夷檀香山的美軍印太司令部如是說。他將在東京會合布林肯，與日本外相茂木敏充及防衞相岸信夫召開2+2安保會議。<br />\n<br />\n日本《讀賣新聞》引述消息。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯和奧斯汀之後會到南韓訪問，早前駐韓美軍司令艾布拉姆斯表示將強化當。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於布林肯回國途中，將於阿拉斯加會晤中共中央政治局委員楊潔篪和外長王毅。拜。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/《讀賣新聞》"},{"pid":"a5de49644c4834d541958d60163121142f948cfb","tid":2447653,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:49:39.000Z","msg":"有 action 既 post 推唔郁，talk 既 post 就第一時間 all talk no action"}]}